Package pegasus.tuple

Interface DoubleTuple

All Superinterfaces:
BaseTuple<Double>, IndexedDoubleIterable, Iterable<Double>, Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
DoubleArrayTuple, DoublePair, DoubleTriple
public interface DoubleTuple extends BaseTuple<Double>, IndexedDoubleIterable
A value-based primitive tuple of double values.
